Cab Booking Web Application

A full-stack Cab Booking web application built as part of a guided development project inspired by Code Astra. This project demonstrates real-world ride-booking system architecture, including user interaction, booking flow, and backend integration.

📌 Project Overview

The Cab Booking App simulates a ride-hailing platform where users can:

Search for rides

Enter pickup & drop locations

View ride options

Confirm bookings

Manage trip details

This project helped in understanding scalable application structure, API handling, and frontend-backend integration.

🛠 Tech Stack
Frontend

React.js

Tailwind CSS

Axios

Backend

Laravel (REST API)

PHP

MySQL

✨ Features

🚗 Ride selection interface

📍 Pickup & Drop input system

💰 Fare estimation logic

🔐 Authentication-ready structure

📦 API-based backend architecture

📱 Responsive UI design

