🚀 Installation Guide
1️⃣ Clone Repository
git clone https://github.com/kumeil99/cab-booking-app.git
cd cab-booking-app
2️⃣ Backend Setup (Laravel)
cd backend
composer install
cp .env.example .env
php artisan key:generate
php artisan migrate
php artisan serve
3️⃣ Frontend Setup (React)
cd frontend
npm install
npm start
